{"type": "article", "id": 26608, "title": "蘑菇型充电器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140112Xt4nemLE6NjHxWMb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这款既是台灯又是手机充电座的 Mushroom Lamp 由 ZISION 工作室和 IDMIX 共同推出。它内置五千毫安时的锂聚合物电池，作为台灯使用时可以持续照明八小时，如果同时为手机充电的的话也能提供五个小时的照明，兼顾了美观的造型以及实用性。这款产品目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/529636401/a-mushroom-lamp-can-charge-your-iphone\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，价格为 69 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140108TmGFit46XUolxCpW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140109ZMAv3Yshf0IxjWya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140110CnaNishflx2PVkYR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63970588\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140111soXzlVbT2GZde5hN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}